Fri May 22 00:00:00 UTC 2026 - bzeller@suse.com

- Initial release of libzypp-glib 0.1.0
  * GLib/GObject C API for zyppng, the next-generation package
    management library
  * Standalone: does not link legacy libzypp.so; bundles zyppng
    as a static archive
  * GObject Introspection support (Zypp-1.0.typelib)
  * Requires Clang 19; targets Tumbleweed and Leap/SLES 16+
